<Defs>

  <ThingDef ParentName="InfinityBigDipperBaseGun">
    <defName>napalm_rocket</defName>
    <label>for altais napalm rocket</label>
    <description>네이팜 로켓포입니다. 원래는 인간한테도 사용했지만 크로노스 메카노이드 알타이스 등장으로 총알이 효과적이지 못해졌기 때문에 네이팜 로켓포를 알타이스 대항용으로 개조했습니다.</description>
    <graphicData>
      <texPath>Things/weapon/Altais weapon/napalm_rocket</texPath>
      <graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
    </graphicData>
    <soundInteract>Shot_Kronosmounting</soundInteract>
    <thingSetMakerTags><li>RewardStandardQualitySuper</li></thingSetMakerTags>
	<equippedAngleOffset>45</equippedAngleOffset>
    <thingCategories Inherit="False">
      <li>Altais_Weapons</li>
    </thingCategories>
	<recipeMaker>
        <researchPrerequisite>Fabrication</researchPrerequisite>
        <recipeUsers Inherit="False">
          <li>FabricationBench</li>
        </recipeUsers>
        <skillRequirements>
          <Crafting>5</Crafting>
        </skillRequirements>
	</recipeMaker>
    <statBases>
      <WorkToMake>42000</WorkToMake>
      <Mass>25</Mass>
      <AccuracyTouch>0.8</AccuracyTouch>
      <AccuracyShort>0.75</AccuracyShort>
      <AccuracyMedium>0.85</AccuracyMedium>
      <AccuracyLong>0.88</AccuracyLong>
      <RangedWeapon_Cooldown>8</RangedWeapon_Cooldown>
    </statBases>
    <costList>
      <Steel>125</Steel>
      <Plasteel>45</Plasteel>
      <ComponentSpacer>3</ComponentSpacer>
    </costList>
    <verbs>
      <li>
        <verbClass>Verb_Shoot</verbClass>
        <hasStandardCommand>true</hasStandardCommand>
        <defaultProjectile>Bullet_napalm_rocket</defaultProjectile>
        <warmupTime>5</warmupTime>
        <minRange>12</minRange> 
        <forcedMissRadius>0.8</forcedMissRadius>
        <burstShotCount>3</burstShotCount>
        <ai_AvoidFriendlyFireRadius>5</ai_AvoidFriendlyFireRadius>
        <ticksBetweenBurstShots>20</ticksBetweenBurstShots>
        <range>32</range>
        <targetParams>
          <canTargetLocations>true</canTargetLocations>
        </targetParams>
        <onlyManualCast>true</onlyManualCast>
        <soundCast>InfernoCannon_Fire</soundCast>
        <soundCastTail>GunTail_Heavy</soundCastTail>
        <muzzleFlashScale>14</muzzleFlashScale>
      </li>
    </verbs>
    <tools>
      <li>
        <label>stock</label>
        <capacities>
          <li>Blunt</li>
        </capacities>
        <power>9</power>
        <cooldownTime>2</cooldownTime>
      </li>
    </tools>
    <weaponTags Inherit="False">
      <li></li>
    </weaponTags>
  </ThingDef>

  <ThingDef ParentName="BaseBullet">
    <defName>Bullet_napalm_rocket</defName>
